  "subject": "Migrate to Java 17 and bump SO parent to 1.19.0",
  "commit_message": "Migrate to Java 17 and bump SO parent to 1.19.0\n\n- Update parent POM from 1.18.0-SNAPSHOT to 1.19.0\n- Set java.version and compiler target to 17\n- Update so-core-version to 1.19.0\n- Update Dockerfile base image to eclipse-temurin:17-jre-alpine\n- Add .mvn/jvm.config with --add-opens for Java 17 module system\n- Remove CryptoUtils usage (class removed in SO 1.19.0)\n- Update test configs with plaintext auth credentials\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4359\nChange-Id: I21c326969dcf48fc34ea60d8e90e9043db26ce3d\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
